WEBVTT

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:14.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God has commanded
us this day;

00:00:14.104 --> 00:00:18.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He has given us
a charge to obey.

00:00:18.895 --> 00:00:23.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At all times,
be ready to impart

00:00:23.770 --> 00:00:27.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The reason for the hope
within your heart.

00:00:27.770 --> 00:00:32.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So preach the Word,
Oh, how vital that all hear!

00:00:32.604 --> 00:00:37.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
As this system’s end draws near.

00:00:37.229 --> 00:00:41.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Help the meek to understand.

00:00:41.729 --> 00:00:46.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Throughout the land!

00:00:49.104 --> 00:00:53.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Seasons of trouble
we will face;

00:00:53.395 --> 00:00:58.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Opposition may bring
shame and disgrace.

00:00:58.270 --> 00:01:03.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Though preaching
may out of season seem,

00:01:03.062 --> 00:01:06.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our trust is in our God,
who is supreme.

00:01:06.979 --> 00:01:11.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So preach the Word,
Oh, how vital that all hear!

00:01:11.812 --> 00:01:16.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
As this system’s end draws near.

00:01:16.395 --> 00:01:20.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Help the meek to understand.

00:01:20.979 --> 00:01:26.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Throughout the land!

00:01:33.229 --> 00:01:37.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Seasons of favor
we will see,

00:01:37.270 --> 00:01:41.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the need for us to teach,
there will be.

00:01:41.729 --> 00:01:46.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The way to salvation
we proclaim

00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:50.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And help to sanctify
Jehovah’s name.

00:01:50.895 --> 00:01:55.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So preach the Word,
Oh, how vital that all hear!

00:01:55.812 --> 00:02:00.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
As this system’s end draws near.

00:02:00.312 --> 00:02:04.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Help the meek to understand.

00:02:04.895 --> 00:02:13.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Preach the Word,
Throughout the land!

